    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.18.4-5_0001"/>
                
                <note type="curatorial">Missouri Collection</note>
                <fw type="curatorial">4</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>Lenzfried-castle, 25.3.39</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Sir!</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Would you be so kind as to write your highly esteemed signature on the enclosed little card. I possess in the castle-archives already the autographs of famous poets and it would be for me a very great honour to get also yours.</p>
                
                <p>I am sorry that it was not possible to get stamps of your country for return-postage; please excuse this.</p>
                
                <p>Thanking you cordially in advance for the great amiability, I am</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>yours respectfully</salute>
                    <signed>Josef Leichtle</signed>
                    <unclear>cand. rer. pol.</unclear>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.18.4-5_0002"/>
                
                <ab type="postmark"><figure><figDesc>Partial Swastika</figDesc></figure> STADT DER BEW<unclear reason="missing"/>  <unclear><figure><figDesc>Partial Swastika</figDesc></figure></unclear> STADT DER<unclear reason="missing"/></ab>
                
                <note place="left"><hi rend="underline">ansd</hi></note> 
                
                <ab type="address">
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Herrn John Gneisenau Neihardt</addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="underline">Branson/Missouri</hi></addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Amerika.</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </ab>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
